{"tid":2321983,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"趙斗淳今出獄丨《許願》原型犯滿頭白髮現身 民眾見強姦犯怒擲石頭","createTime":"2020-12-12T03:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T02:52:16.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"81f743d6a7775b12d422fa85a1afa47a4d650742","tid":2321983,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T03:09:06.000Z","msg":"監獄門前聚集數十人<br />\n今早在首爾九老區南部監獄門前已聚集了30至40人，有10多名男女更躺在馬路上，一度想阻止趙斗淳乘坐官用車輛離開。當接載趙斗淳的車輛駛出時，一眾圍觀者即起哄，並邊罵邊向車輛擲豆腐、石頭等。在監獄12年的趙斗淳出獄後乘坐車子到京畿道安山水原保護觀察所安山分所，提交保護觀察的申請書，辦理完手續後他就返回安山市與妻子同住。而事隔12年終於首次公開露面的趙斗淳在警員的押送下抵達觀察所，他戴上口罩及帽子現身，可見已經68歲的他滿頭白髮，他現身後有鞠躬行禮。不過當記者問到他「你反省了嗎？」時，他就未有發言，同時可見他手上緊握一個桔仔。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201212/YGJWF6J4GNDQFFCSEX6L66TUCM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201212%2FYGJWF6J4GNDQFFCSEX6L66TUCM%2F&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=c78baaaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201212%2FYGJWF6J4GNDQFFCSEX6L66TUCM%2F&h=2dc74f3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201212/YGJWF6J4GNDQFFCSEX6L66TUCM/</a>"},{"pid":"1031ef7cde53adc94594ee340ddfad3d9384fbda","tid":2321983,"uid":39492,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T03:11:00.000Z","msg":"當年個細路女⋯⋯依家點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n造成永久性創傷<br />\n<br />\n我係個女仔，應該安樂死算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a204ae61e66095d15f276252000024a010acb7","tid":2321983,"uid":232228,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T03:13:14.000Z","msg":"佢應該好快俾啲鄰居搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgm